name: #MD1 Setyaki
description:
Setyaki, the chieftain of Narayani Sena, a valiant warrior clan famous for their bravery. Setyaki is one of Pandavas most valuable ally as he is brave, loyal and passionate.
Setyaki's highlight in the Great War is when he single-handedly defends Yudhistira against tens of thousands of Kurava warriors led by Burisrawa. Setyaki able to slay Burisrawa at the end, with the help of Arjuna.

Setyaki is one of the few survivors of the Great War.
